!! Use Case
* wget scripts from https://dropbox.com/.../xxx
* chmod
* change config if needed
* run it
* read setup report
* further manual actions according to the report

!! Various Requirements
* For Package Management
** update repository list
** update repository cache

* For OS Misc
** set proxy

* For Bash
** .bashrc
** .profile

* For VIM
** install vim
** .vimrc
** plugins
*** ctag
*** taglist

* For Development
** install gcc
** install Make
** For git
*** install git
*** add ssh key to github and gitorious
*** git clone pre-defined repositories

* For VNC
** install vncserver
** start a vncserver
** .vnc

* For ssh
** install sshd
** start sshd service
** generate key in .ssh/

* For nokia firewall
** install required programs
** config
